The paper discusses the advancements in Natural Language Processing (NLP) using deep learning methods and models. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also mentions the usage of deep learning methods in areas such as Computer Vision (cs.CV), Automatic Speech Recognition (cs.SD), and NLP (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the utilization of data-driven strategies, which falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
